<h1>A-G Requirements</h1>
<p>
  To attend a University of California (UC) or a California State University(CSU), <br>
  all high school students need to complete the A-G requirements. The following<br>
  are a list of the required subjects and number of years.
</p>
<p>
  You must receive a grade of C or better. You can also use test scores. The classes must<br>
  be from the approved list.
  Click <a href="http://admission.universityofcalifornia.edu/freshman/requirements/a-g-requirements/">here</a>
  for more information from UC website.
</p>
